<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    
    <title>IDE Jutge.org - Components Overview</title>
    
    <!-- css, javascript -->
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/fonts/UbuntuMono.css'>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <script src="/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="jtg-doc-title">
      <div class="jtg-doc-title-box">
      <span class="jtg-doc-title-span">
        ide.jutge - IDE Components Overview
      </span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="jtg-doc-page">
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <img src="/img/doc/ide-components.png" alt="IDE Components" class="jtg-doc-img">
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-toc">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <ul>
            <li>1 - <a href="#menu-bar">Menu Bar</a></li>
            <li>2 - <a href="#c++-toolbar">C++ Toolbar</a></li>
            <li>3 - <a href="#code-editor">Code Editor</a></li>
            <li>4 - <a href="#status-bar">Status Bar</a></li>
            <li>5 - <a href="#c++-panel">C++ Panel</a></li>
            <li>6 - <a href="#terminal-diagnostics">Terminal/Diagnostics</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h2" id="menu-bar">
        <span>1 - Menu Bar</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h3" id="file-menu">
        <span class="fonb">File Menu</span>
        <img src="/img/doc/file-menu.png" alt="File Menu" class="flor">
        <div class="jtg-doc-sep"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <p><span class="fonb">New</span>: Clears the code editor.</p>
          <p><span class="fonb">Open</span>: Open a file in the editor.</p>
          <p><span class="fonb">Save</span>: Save the code to a file in the <i>Downloads</i> folder.</p>
          <p><span class="fonb">Import</span>: No function yet.</p>
          <p><span class="fonb">Export</span>: No function yet.</p>
          <p><span class="fonb">C++ templates</span>: Open a C++ program template in the editor.</p>
          <p>The provided C++ program templates are:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Hello world!: <i>The "Hello world" program in C++.</i></li>
            <li>Fill in a vector: <i>About C ++ STL (Standard Template Library) vector, and standard input/output.</i></li>
            <li>Iterative GCD: <i>Calculates the greatest common denominator of two numbers, iteratively.</i></li>
            <li>Correct parenthesization?: <i>Answers the question using an STL stack.</i></li>
            <li>Fibonacci in a vector: <i>Calculate Fibonacci numbers using an iterative technique.</i></li>
            <li>Recursive factorial: <i>Calculate the factorial of a number using a recursive technique.</i></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h3" id="edit-menu">
        <span class="fonb">Edit Menu</span>
        <img src="/img/doc/edit-menu.png" alt="Edit Menu" class="flor">
        <div class="jtg-doc-sep"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <p><span class="fonb">Undo</span>: Undoes the last change in the editor.</p>
          <p><span class="fonb">Redo</span>: Redoes the last undone change.</p>
          <p><span class="fonb">Select all</span>: Selects all the code in the editor.</p>
          <br>
          <p>
          The traditional <i>Cut</i>, <i>Copy</i> and <i>Paste</i> commands are not available as Edit menu options,
          but can be triggered using the standard key shortcuts.
          </p>
          <p>
          <i>Accessing the system clipboard via JavaScript is considered an
unsafe operation: scripts could erase and replace the contents of the clipboard
(data loss issue), and also read the contents of the clipboard (security and
privacy issue).</i>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h3" id="view-menu">
        <span class="fonb">View Menu</span>
        <img src="/img/doc/view-menu.png" alt="View Menu" class="flor">
        <div class="jtg-doc-sep"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <p><span class="fonb">Font size</span>: Set the code editor's font size.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Smaller: 10px</li>
            <li>Small: 12px</li>
            <li>Normal: 14px</li>
            <li>Large: 16px</li>
            <li>Larger: 18px</li>
          </ul>
          <p><span class="fonb">IDE themes</span>: Change <b>ide.jutge</b>'s theme.</p>
          <p>jQuery EasyUI provides different themes:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Default themes:<br><i>Default, Bootstrap, Metro, Gray, Black, Material.</i></li>
            <li>UI themes:<br><i>Cupertino, Pepper grinder, Dark hive.</i></li>
            <li>Metro themes:<br><i>Blue, Gray, Green, Orange, Red.</i></li>
          </ul>
          <p><span class="fonb">Editor themes</span>: Change the editor's theme.</p>
          <p>Ace editor provides different themes:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Light themes:<br><i>Chrome, Clouds, Crimson editor, Dawn, Dreamweaver, Eclipse, GitHub,
            IPlastic, KatzenMilch, Kuroir, Solarized light, SQL server, Textmate, Tomorrow, XCode.</i></li>
            <li>Dark themes:<br><i>Ambiance, Chaos, Clouds midnight, Cobalt, Idle fingers, Kr theme,
            Merbivore, Merbivore soft, Mono industrial, Monokai, Pastel on dark, Solarized dark, 
            Terminal, Tomorrow night, Tomorrow night blue, Tomorrow night bright, Tomorrow night 80s,
            Twilight, Vibrant ink.</i></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h3" id="help-menu">
        <span class="fonb">Help Menu</span>
        <img src="/img/doc/help-menu.png" alt="Help Menu" class="flor">
        <div class="jtg-doc-sep"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <p><span class="fonb">Help</span>: Links to the IDE's documentation.</p>
          <p><span class="fonb">About</span>: General information about <b>ide.jutge</b>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h2" id="c++-toolbar">
        <span>2 - C++ Toolbar</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h3" id="exec-selector">
        <span class="fonb">Execution Selector</span>
        <img src="/img/doc/exec-menu.png" alt="Execution Selector" class="flor">
        <div class="jtg-doc-sep"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <p><span class="fonb">Run</span>: Execute the program.</p>
          <p><span class="fonb">Debug</span>: Debug the program.</p>
          <p><span class="fonb">Slow motion</span>: Debug the program one line at a time.</p>
          <p><span class="fonb">Valgrind</span>: Run the program through <i>Valgrind</i> to find memory-related errors.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h3" id="debug-controls">
        <span class="fonb">Debug Controls</span>
        <div class="jtg-doc-sep"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <table>
            <tr>
              <th>Button</th>
              <th>Command</th>
              <th>Description</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="talc"><img src="/img/Continue.png" alt="Continue Button"> / <img src="/img/Pause.png" alt="Pause Button"></td>
              <td class="talc"><b>Continue/Pause</b></td>
              <td>Continue or pause the program's execution.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="talc"><img src="/img/Kill.png" alt="Stop Button"></td>
              <td class="talc"><b>Stop</b></td>
              <td>Kill the executing program.<br><i>Available in all execution modes.</i></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="talc"><img src="/img/StepOver.png" alt="Step Over Button"></td>
              <td class="talc"><b>Step Over</b></td>
              <td>Advance the program’s execution to the next line of code, ignoring function calls.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="talc"><img src="/img/StepInto.png" alt="Step Into Button"></td>
              <td class="talc"><b>Step Into</b></td>
              <td>Advance the program’s execution to the next line if it is not a function call.<br>
              If it is, stop at the first instruction of the called function.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="talc"><img src="/img/StepOut.png" alt="Step Out Button"></td>
              <td class="talc"><b>Step Out</b></td>
              <td>Resume the execution of the program until the current function is exited.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="talc"><img src="/img/doc/interval-scroller.png" alt="Interval Scroller"></td>
              <td class="talc"><b>Slow Motion Interval</b></td>
              <td>Set the interval for the <i>Slow motion</i> execution mode (1 to 10 seconds).</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h2" id="code-editor">
        <span>3 - Code Editor</span>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <p>Fully featured code editor with C++ syntax highlighting.</p>
          <p>
          Click on the left side of the gutter to insert/remove breakpoints
          (<img src="/img/jtg-breakpoint.png" alt="Breakpoint Icon">).
          </p>
          <p>
          The 
          <img src='data:image/png;base64,' alt="Error Icon">
          icon marks compilation errors, and the
          <img src='data:image/png;base64,' alt="Warning Icon">
          icon marks warnings.
          </p>
          <img src="/img/doc/editor-panel.png" alt="Code Editor">
        </div>
      </div>
      
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h2" id="status-bar">
        <span>4 - Status Bar</span>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <p>Located under the code editor, this bar displays various messages about executed commands.</p>
          <img src="/img/doc/status-bar.png" alt="Status Bar">
        </div>
      </div>
      
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h2" id="c++-panel">
        <span>5 - C++ Panel</span>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
        <p>Features provided in this panel are not available when executing in <i>Run</i> mode.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-h3" id="variables-tab">
        <span class="fonb">Variables Tab</span>
        <div class="jtg-doc-sep"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <img src="/img/doc/variables-tab.png" alt="Variables Tab">
          <p>Provides a datagrid to show the program’s variables in the current execution context.</p>
          <p>This datagrid is filled when the program pauses, and cleared when it resumes.</p>
          <p>During a pause, program variables may be altered by editing the corresponding cell in the datagrid.</p>
          <p id="modifiable-variable-types">Only variables of the following types may be modified:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>int</li>
            <li>float</li>
            <li>double</li>
            <li>char</li>
            <li>bool</li>
            <li>std::__cxx11::string</li>
            <li>short</li>
            <li>long</li>
            <li>long double</li>
            <li>long long</li>
            <li>wchar_t</li>
            <li>unsigned char</li>
            <li>signed char</li>
            <li>unsigned int</li>
            <li>signed int</li>
            <li>short int</li>
            <li>unsigned short int</li>
            <li>signed short int</li>
            <li>long int</li>
            <li>signed long int</li>
            <li>unsigned long int</li>
            <li>signed long long</li>
            <li>unsigned long long</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h3" id="frames-tab">
        <span class="fonb">Frames Tab</span>
        <div class="jtg-doc-sep"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <img src="/img/doc/frames-tab.png" alt="Frames Tab">
          <p>Provides a table to show the program’s call stack —that is, the
          chain of function calls that have been invoked.</p>
          <p>This table is filled when the program pauses (usually because of a
          breakpoint being hit), and cleared when it resumes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h3" id="exprs-tab">
        <span class="fonb">Expressions Tab</span>
        <div class="jtg-doc-sep"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <img src="/img/doc/exprs-tab.png" alt="Expressions Tab">
          <p>Much like the variables datagrid, expressions in the datagrid are evaluated 
          and their results shown when the program pauses.</p>
          <p>When the program resumes, the results in the grid are cleared.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h3" id="valgrind-tab">
        <span class="fonb">Valgrind Tab</span>
        <div class="jtg-doc-sep"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <img src="/img/doc/valgrind-tab.png" alt="Valgrind Tab">
          <p>Provides a table of memory-related errors once the program terminates.</p>
          <p>Only avalilable when executing in <i>Valgrind</i> mode.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      
      <div class="jtg-doc-h2" id="terminal-diagnostics">
        <span>6 - Terminal/Diagnostics</span>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-h3" id="terminal-tab">
        <span class="fonb">Terminal Tab</span>
        <div class="jtg-doc-sep"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <img src="/img/doc/term-tab.png" alt="Terminal Tab">
          <p>The <i>Terminal</i> is used to read from and write to the executing C++ program.</p>
          <p>The <img src="/img/clear-term.png" alt="Clear Termial Button"> button clears the <i>Terminal</i>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-h3" id="diagnostics-tab">
        <span class="fonb">Diagnostics Tab</span>
        <div class="jtg-doc-sep"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="jtg-doc-text">
        <div class="jtg-doc-par">
          <img src="/img/doc/diagnostics-tab.png" alt="Diagnostics Tab">
          <p>Provides a table which will display compilation errors, if any are found.</p>
          <p>Clicking on an error row will highlight the corresponding line in the code editor.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <%> footer %>      
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
